                "value": 0.99
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The target was produced by",
                "evaporating about 10 ug/cm2 Li-F(99% enriched in 7-Li)",
                "on 0.5 mm thick copper backing. The thickness of the",
                "target was 3.7+-0.3 keV at 224-keV protons.",
                "Composition of the target:",
                "Li - (1.73+-0.15) x 10**17 atoms/cm2",
                "Boron- 0.41 x 10**17  atoms/cm2",
                "Carbon-0.07 x 10**17  atoms/cm2",
                "Oxygen-0.05 x 10**17  atoms/cm2"
              ]
            }
          ],
